            <h3>My Vision</h3>
            <p>This is the beginning of <strong>TaiwanMe</strong>.</p>
            <p>Although my physical journey often shuttles between just two points—Taipei and Pingtung—my heart has expanded to embrace the entire island of Taiwan.</p>
            
